verbose_text: Moreover, the rate of PMA triggered loss of TACE from the cell surface was not significantly different (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A and S2B), and dynasore did not rescue shedding in the iRhom2 Dead mutant, confirming that defective endocytosis or sorting to the lysosome could not account for the TACE shedding defect (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY D).
